doc.after: The major local newspaper is the Amarillo Globe News owned by Morris Communications was a combination of three newspapers Amarillo Daily News Amarillo Globe and Amarillo Times Other publications include a local monthly magazine dealing with city and regional issues in the Amarillo area called Accent West The American Quarter Horse Association publishes two monthly publications The American Quarter Horse Journal and The American Quarter Horse Racing Journal HISPANIC Newspaper El Mensajero owned by Dr Ramon Godoy started printing in 1989
